+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
                                                         Office Web App Server
+++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++

1. /hosting/discovery
OWA server expose this public facing page to inform of all its supported actions (filetypes and urls for example).
Browsing yourOWApublic.com/hosting/discovery from any browser return an XML page.

2. PowerShell: Get-OfficeWebAppsFarm
The Get-OfficeWebAppsFarm cmdlet returns details about the OfficeWebAppsFarm object that the current server is a member of :
https://technet.microsoft.com/en-us/library/jj219434.aspx

